<view class="top">
  <view class="content">
    <view class="show-card">
      <image class="show" src="../../images/show05.jpg" />
    </view>
    <view class="title">选择卡面</view>
    <view class="card-list">
      <view class="cards" wx:for="{{cardLists}}" wx:key="{{index}}">
        <image class="props" src="{{item}}" />
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="title title1">选择礼品</view>
    <view class="gift-list">
      <view class="giftCards" wx:for="{{giftLists}}" wx:key="{{index}}">
        <view class="price">{{item}} 元</view>
        <view class="text">星礼卡</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="center"></view>
<view class="footer">
  <view class="pro">
    <view class="name">适用门店</view>
    <view class="desc">查看全部门店</view>
  </view>
  <view class="pro">
    <view class="name">可用时段</view>
    <view class="desc starCard">2017.02.14-2020.02.14 周一至周日全天</view>
  </view>
  <view class="pro line3">
    <view class="name">使用须知</view>
    <view class="desc starCard right">
      <view>-电子星礼卡的有效期为激活(或末次充值，若适用)之日起三年;</view>
      <view>-您可以在中国大陆境内任意星巴克门店(部分门店除外，详情请见《星巴克用星说社交礼品须知》)购买其出售的指定商品；</view>
      <view>-此电子星礼卡可以多次适用，不可兑换现金，不找零；</view>
      <view>-使用电子星礼卡在门店消费时，同时出示有效星享卡累积星星。</view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="pro buy">
    <view class="name">购买须知</view>
    <view class="desc">查看内容</view>
  </view>
</view>
<view class="button">
  <button class="btn" type="primary">购买并赠送</button>
</view>